{{monster info}}
==Useful Info==
'''Vampire magi''' are irritating [[undead]] casters who hound you with summoned undead allies and [[draining]] bolts. Although only slightly stronger physically than a standard [[vampire (monster)|vampire]], their spells are much more irritating. They can be found throughout [[the Crypt]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*[[Negative energy]] resistance seriously hampers their ability to damage you.
